claim.claim-text:
An anvil assembly delivery system comprising:
an anvil assembly including a center rod and an anvil head assembly secured to the center rod;
a flexible tube having a first end configured for oral insertion into a patient and a second end, the anvil assembly being connected to the second end of the flexible tube;
a retrieval suture connected to the head assembly, the retrieval suture being positioned to extend from the anvil assembly in a direction opposite to the flexible tube; and
a spacer supported on the retrieval suture adjacent the anvil head assembly, the spacer being dimensioned to prevent the suture from being clamped between the anvil head assembly and a stapling instrument and becoming trapped in a staple line.
